Text.Value: I appreciate that - but I can't help how I feel. Sorry.
Not if it's with him. Not interested.
What kind of services does a Drow in the city provide exactly?
What kind of services do you provide?
Forget I said anything. Let's drop this.
Not so for us.
I want both of you. At the same time.
I worked in this business in the Underdark, but it grew to festering monotony.
I can barely afford new underclothes at the moment, yet alone this.
I suppose I haven't ticked incest off the moral atrocities to-do list yet.
In that case, we will require two of you. And indeed, I suggest it because I have never seen a creature as fair as this pale beau beside you.

EditorData.logicalname: UNROMANCED ASTARION PRESENT, NO PARTNER PRESENT

Text.Value: You had to spoil the fun, didn't you?
Since I came to the surface, I purchased an enchantment to bless me with infertility, if that soothes your mind.
I'm glad. Provided we survive, there's plenty of nights yet to come.
Can't fault you for being clear about limits. It can be just the two of us.
Maybe I would like to share it with you, then.
I want to hire you, beautiful lad.
You have but to ask, and we can grant you a moment of pleasure.
Eugh. Well, I am certainly not hiring both of you at once.
What a world. I never dreamed I'd be on the paying end in a brothel.
I was forced into it, but it sounds as if you weren't.
Don't waste a moment, bring your partner. I want to see what you can do.
Perhaps once we have saved more gold another adventure will begin. We've had busier days, but life is comfortable here with Mamzell.
As the rising sun.
My apologies, Astarion, we should correct that mistake!
But I hope you keep coming back to Mamzell's for the drinks!
Menzoberranzan Love Trick? But you are Seldarine drow, why are you fooling your customers?
I'll come back when I can afford to squander our hard-earned gold.
Life is prosperous. I am much happier kissing the many lips of the surface than tending a field or manning a shop.
As long as you are here of your own free will.
Couldn't get us off your mind, could you?

EditorData.logicalname: Has met, didn't hire, Clicked on female

Text.Value: *Menzoberranzan love magic - a formidable practice, usually only reserved for pleasing the most insatiable matriarchs in the city of spiders.*
Part with the coin.
Degenerate.
An intriguing pair. Takes me back to my youth...
Don't worry, I wouldn't ask such a thing of you.
You make a tempting offer, but for your safety, I've got to say no.
I feel the same way.
Great, let's do it.
Of course you came back! I never doubted you would.

EditorData.logicalname: Has met, didn't hire, Clicked on male

Text.Value: You don't actually lie with one another... do you?
Enjoy yourself, of course, but I dearly hope you aren't only having sex because we haven't in a while.
Sorry dear, I want to hire them both for myself.
My, my, I can tell you are a special one from a single glance.
You're welcome if you have the coin. ([GEN_CheckMagicPocketGold_6057ad05-9492-4630-9f0a-be548b134c54])
Horrible. Unfathomably so.
Spoilsport.
Ah, a person of taste indeed.
A new face! Looking for another chapter of dirty lore for your biography?
You are back with your partner. It would be a delight to spend time with both of you.
While it's a fascinating prospect, I'd like you all to myself... at least the first time.
If your beloved one wants to join, we could work out something to our mutual satisfaction.
Well I suppose it would do no good to back out now. Let us begin this little anthropological study, if we must.
I'm very sorry to hear that... There are many courtesans who end up in the business out of unfortunate necessity. We, however, could easily take up other work if we wished.
Damn Helsik's portal, orgies are where the money goes!
You can cut them if you want, dear.
I'd like to hire your services, my lady.
You won't be upset if I choose to partake?
You'll just have to see what is in store.
I don't like to share. Lay a finger on them, and I'll cut you.
Ah, you're lucky, sister.
Ahem. Sorry, pet, I'm not quite comfortable with doing this again yet.
No wonder, look at us. We're immaculate.
There's an idea. If you're comfortable sharing... so am I.
Go forth! Many nights with your partner await you! Our work is done, and we must attend to other clients.
What? Really? What could they possibly offer you that I can't do better?
We will only allow that if we know there is an evening of exceptional pleasure awaiting us. Usually one darling alone is not enough to match the two of us.
Two of us, two of you. Four gorgeous people.
More than interested, if you feel the same.
The more the merrier!
I would have liked to, but I understand.
Trust me, you don't want to miss my signature Menzoberranzan Love Trick.
Mamzell Amira said you could provide me with a gift for helping her.
I might regret this, but why not.
You're back! Why don't we try again? Throw our bodies back into the ring!
Interested, Halsin?
Eugh, don't be so nice to me! It makes me want to be nice back.
Mamzell Amira said you could offer your services as a gift of her thanks.
Come hither. We have a room upstairs.
Sorry, Halsin, I was hoping this would just be between us three.
I would like to hire both of you. And I hope my partner will join us as well.
A once-in-a-lifetime moment of passion. Every day. What could be better? Don't you want to try it?
And I don't want to share you.
What was it like?
This is getting to be too much. I'll pass, after all.
I might enjoy watching you tangled up with the drow, as long as I was five paces back.
After years working here, though, Mamzell is like family, and makes sure our clients treat us with as much respect as we want to be treated with.
Cough up the money.
Return to us if you have a lover willing to take part.
I'd rather tangle with a dragon than get tangled in all those limbs.
I'd have to restrain myself far more than any play-bindings do if I worked in another field. This is a place where I can be myself boundlessly.
You have had my sister, now let my cock bring you the deliverance of the astral plane!

EditorData.logicalname: Had intimacy with OTHER sibling, Clicked on male

Text.Value: Charming!
And don't worry, I'll dart out if I don't enjoy it faster than I used to run from the sun.
It was not my work itself that has ever been a challenge to me, merely the circumstances.
So long as all are willing, I see no reason why we should deny ourselves...
I will return when I can afford to debase my party's coin.
Good.
Let's go, this is thrilling!
Are you sure this is where you want to be?
Whatever you wish! But with another pair is the only way we will both be happy to join you.
And is that your partner with you? What a gorgeous couple... perhaps we could come to an agreement.
I try not to think about it any longer.
Don't you want a change?
You might have a good time, if you don't overthink it. Only if you want, though.
Don't be shy.
My Mezzoberranzan love is always cocked aready.
I'd like to try doing things like this again, now I'm free to find my own desires.
I'm ready!
A shame, but either one of us will be ready for you, if you wish to have us.
Darling, we are not fooling anyone. Unless you pay for me to make a fool of you.

And there is no society on this planet more laterally, imaginatively, and confusingly depraved as that of Baldur's Gate. Although of late, I do feel I've seen everything. Perhaps you'll show me something new?
I value affection over fun, a lasting memory over a passing fancy. This is our story, not theirs.
I'll eat you right up.
Bah. You would break our bond for the sake of laying this - this is'lak?
Ah, I was hoping to see you again.
I'd prefer you didn't do this. If I'm not enough for you, I could always conjure us some kind of non-sentient companion.
Leave.
There must be a sprinkling shower of gold, first. Ahem. Coin. ([GEN_CheckMagicPocketGold_3_01f129ea-b4dc-44b6-8154-9a948f876a82])
Leave.
Agreement? What kind of agreement?
As you wish. I'm sure I can find berth elsewhere...
My... my apologies for prying.
There must be some devious thoughts in your mind we can help you explore.
Well, Sorn, you sound like a charming man. Let's go up together.
Pleasure is what I know, and what I do best. Here, I work to create it anew for myself each eve.
Nor mine, thanks.
I thought we were weaving our own tale, you and me. Don't turn your back on it.
How does a Drow end up in a place like this?
How did you end up here?
Sorry, friend. But you look like you can't take what I mete out. Bring someone with a rear of cast-iron.
I'm broke - I'll come back when I can copulate away the party's savings.
You two look uncannily alike.
Sorry, Halsin, I was hoping this would just be between us three.
Why are you interested in my partner?
You have returned... I hope you are all right after leaving. We are always happy to try again.
You should learn to flaunt your body - you look great.
This way. We have a room upstairs over yonder side.
Our bodies will haunt your dreams.
What do you think, silly? Love of course! Hot and vulgar with me, or sweet and sincere with my sister.
That's a bit much for me.
What an idea!
You know my feelings - nature's impulses must be pursued. Do as you will, with my blessing.
Ha! We are quite accustomed to working with each other, if you change your mind.
Perhaps I shouldn't do this, never mind.
We can make up a little show of kissing each other, but when we are hired at the same time, there are often many other clients in the room to attend to.
Should I be jealous? At least you have good taste.
This is not for me.
Perhaps you'd care for a little extra company...

EditorData.logicalname: HALSIN PRESENT EVEN IF NOT PARTNERED

Text.Value: Just what I had to do to get by.
It was a bad idea. I'm sorry.
Oh, I suspect we shall be more than merry...
Dish out the money.
Consider yourself invited! Combined, we've had five hundred years to hone our talents - let's put them to bad use.
Well, there are two of us, aren't there? Use your imagination.
If this goes ahead, her luck will run out rather quickly.
The entirety of drow culture is obsessed with bondage beyond reason. While such activities have their charms, I yearned to reach greater depths.
Leave.
Upset? I guess not, as long as everyone's, you know - above board. I get the appeal in theory, but the reality makes me want to take a lye bath.
Have fun, soldier. Leave something left for me later, ey?
I used to work as a courtesan back home, and my sister as an artisanal masseuse, but men are treated like dogs by the Underdark's matriarchs, so we fled.
Maybe not, after all.
I know that look in your eye. Since being with me, you feel as if you are a Northdark Cavern: a hole that can only be filled by Drow.
We are twins.
I'm glad you've found a place you feel safe.
I won't pretend the thought hasn't crossed my mind once or twice... or more than that.
I'm having second thoughts, sorry.
Without the fungal infestations, I hope.
Silly, we are the gift. One free ride with me or my brother.
A brother. And a sister. At the same time. Yeah - no. You do your thing, but that's not mine.
I'll be a little treat for you, then.
No, no. I want romance, not - not debauchery.
Don't worry, Gale. We're not asking your tressym to join us.
We found surfacers crave the body of a Drow like a drug. Life is easy in our line of work.
For being a friend who helped Amira, we will charge a little less. ([GEN_CheckMagicPocketGold_6057ad05-9492-4630-9f0a-be548b134c54])
Are you sure?
Exquisite! You know the price, right? ([GEN_CheckMagicPocketGold_6057ad05-9492-4630-9f0a-be548b134c54])
If you're truly pleased with the work here, I can't judge you.
I've already got a partner, and that's plenty for me, thanks.
You're adorable even when you're teasing me. But I must decline.
Delicious.
There are so many who come to me speaking of a fixation that no one else has ever been able to share with them... and never will again.
This is all a bit much for me. Back home in Waterdeep, I prefer to have Tara leave the room before I undress.
No, Halsin! Tame yourself!
Aren't you at risk of inbreeding, if you keep working together?
Fine, hog them all to yourself. Perhaps I'll find amusement elsewhere.
So eager! You're delicious.
Fork it over.
On second thought, this is a bad idea.
But, our leader here has made the dire mistake of failing to sleep with me so far, and it's a mistake I have been aching to correct.
As you wish. I'm sure I can find berth elsewhere...
Not for me, but thanks.
You have a type, don't you? Elven prostitutes? Again? It's rather embarrassing, dear.

EditorData.NodeContext: whispers 'prostitues' pretending it's a scandalous notion

Text.Value: I do not share what is mine. And I will not be shared.
Menzoberranzan Love Trick? But you are Seldarine drow, why are you fooling your customers?
Though I estimate I could take seven to twelve drow on my own, I'm happy to start with one.
I couldn't have said it any better.
Or perhaps you have greater ambitions yet.
I was talking about cutting you.
Maybe this isn't the best idea. I'll say goodbye.
We want both of you, silly! At the same time.
It's all right, I promise. But I hope when the sun sets and the stars rise, your dreams always lead to me.
I would like to spend time with you, lady Nym.
Your gold, and your loins. Not for me to dictate what you do with either.
Good.
You survived my brother? Let me know if you want to have a more calming time with me.

Text.Value: I was once in your position, in a way.

Synopsis: Three-way dialog with both dapper drow twins in the taproom. The player can hire either of them or both, if they have a partner with them.
